{"title":"荐歌：没有名字的夜晚（夏日入侵企画）","slug":"荐歌：没有名字的夜晚（夏日入侵企画）","date":"2022-04-29T14:31:28.000Z","updated":"2022-04-29T14:34:00.933Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：没有名字的夜晚（夏日入侵企画）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。周末愉快！假期愉快！虽说是拼凑出来的小长假，单好歹是能彻底放松个几天了~过了这个小长假就可能正式步入夏天了，趁着这两天降温好好熬个夜，再好好睡个大懒觉。<br>","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>周末愉快！假期愉快！</p>\n<p>虽说是拼凑出来的小长假，单好歹是能彻底放松个几天了~</p>\n<p>过了这个小长假就可能正式步入夏天了，趁着这两天降温好好熬个夜，再好好睡个大懒觉。<br><span id=\"more\"></span></p>\n<p>本周荐歌《没有名字的夜晚》，来自夏日入侵企画。（<strong>可以在网易云听</strong>）</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1849674035&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n\n<p>慵懒、惬意，正如歌词中的点睛之笔——“<strong>时间虚度又如何</strong>”。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">黄昏日落世界坠入光河</span><br><span class=\"line\">车流的轮廓 浪潮起落</span><br><span class=\"line\">匆忙人群 鱼跃 而过</span><br><span class=\"line\">身影间温柔拉扯</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">星幕下沉呼吸缱绻炙热</span><br><span class=\"line\">城市的脉络 纠葛交错</span><br><span class=\"line\">蒸汽泡沫 光影斑驳</span><br><span class=\"line\">恍惚中难以捉摸</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">空气与记忆重合</span><br><span class=\"line\">有一种落寞失而复得</span><br><span class=\"line\">随刹那花火湮没</span><br><span class=\"line\">依旧期待转折</span><br><span class=\"line\">时间虚度又如何</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">也许是夏夜意外的可能</span><br><span class=\"line\">温热的风却来的情理之中</span><br><span class=\"line\">微醺霓虹失焦的街灯</span><br><span class=\"line\">人潮仍汹涌</span><br><span class=\"line\">不知道该去怎么形容</span><br><span class=\"line\">闪烁的梦 什么永恒</span><br><span class=\"line\">此刻的莫名自我感动</span><br><span class=\"line\">不需要人懂</span><br><span class=\"line\">迎着风</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n","more":"</p>\n<p>本周荐歌《没有名字的夜晚》，来自夏日入侵企画。（<strong>可以在网易云听</strong>）</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1849674035&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n\n<p>慵懒、惬意，正如歌词中的点睛之笔——“<strong>时间虚度又如何</strong>”。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">黄昏日落世界坠入光河</span><br><span class=\"line\">车流的轮廓 浪潮起落</span><br><span class=\"line\">匆忙人群 鱼跃 而过</span><br><span class=\"line\">身影间温柔拉扯</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">星幕下沉呼吸缱绻炙热</span><br><span class=\"line\">城市的脉络 纠葛交错</span><br><span class=\"line\">蒸汽泡沫 光影斑驳</span><br><span class=\"line\">恍惚中难以捉摸</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">空气与记忆重合</span><br><span class=\"line\">有一种落寞失而复得</span><br><span class=\"line\">随刹那花火湮没</span><br><span class=\"line\">依旧期待转折</span><br><span class=\"line\">时间虚度又如何</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">也许是夏夜意外的可能</span><br><span class=\"line\">温热的风却来的情理之中</span><br><span class=\"line\">微醺霓虹失焦的街灯</span><br><span class=\"line\">人潮仍汹涌</span><br><span class=\"line\">不知道该去怎么形容</span><br><span class=\"line\">闪烁的梦 什么永恒</span><br><span class=\"line\">此刻的莫名自我感动</span><br><span class=\"line\">不需要人懂</span><br><span class=\"line\">迎着风</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>","categories":[{"name":"人文","path":"api/categories/人文.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"人文","path":"api/tags/人文.json"},{"name":"荐歌","path":"api/tags/荐歌.json"}]}